data.description: Marvelously Charming Two-Story Home in Central Southwest Houston! Situated in a quiet community just steps from Cogburn Park-City Park West, this 4BR/2.5BA, 1,902sqft property immediately delights with a beautiful brick façade, tidy landscaping, and neighborly sidewalks. Designed for universal appeal, the interior features an organically flowing layout, stylish wood flooring, wide doorways, a large living room, and a fully equipped kitchen boasting stainlesssteel appliances, gas stove, wood cabinetry, breakfast nook, and a pantry. Dog-friendly with privacy fencing, the backyard also enjoys a concrete patio, greenspace, and plenty of room for playing. Bask in the spacious primary bedroom with ample closet space and an attached en suite with a soaking tub, separate shower, and dual sinks. Additional considerations include an attached two-car garage, laundry area, only 10-miles to Downtown Houston, near shopping, restaurants, Starbucks, and schools, and so much more!
